                                 String dateStr,
                                 String xpath,

Checks if the timezone on the given dateStr is zero. If so, adds a new reason with the given xpath and type to the list of reasons.

Parameters:
reasons - list to add to if timezone is zero
dateStr - date string to check
xpath - xpath of the element
